{"tid":2081032,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"港漫文戲第一人牛佬全新鉅著《勝利人生》討論區（1）","createTime":"2020-06-27T01:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T07:30:41.000Z","uid":4389,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0908dcfaa95b2d23d577bb2208dceb4e64bee6","tid":2081032,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3AfneF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3AfneF.jpg&h=23928c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNqva7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNqva7F.png&h=035d287b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkKf6F6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbkKf6F6.png&h=defd0f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勝利重點：民初陳浩南係個車伕，帶領住一個小幫叫虎幫，有兩個忠心嘍囉仲有廿幾人跟埋佢劈友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地劈友有句口號，叫勝利人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一次同蛇頭幫衝突，將小頭目青蛇打敗，結果將三個蛇頭引出，睇嚟又有一場龍爭虎鬥⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味牛佬，仲以為抖咗兩個月。會有咩煥然一新，結果換湯不換藥。第一期好多格，又無咩影印道，不過要睇多幾期嚟評價。<br />\n<br />\n而家本書唔使套膠袋，咁點描寫黑幫情節？<br />\n<br />\n況且炒咗咁多助理，出個制作組個名就算，炒人嘅錢拎嚟搵個編劇有幾難？"},{"pid":"e91c0c158b21d1bc7b7d0fc87bcf9c27250f6708","tid":2081032,"uid":220431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T01:58:01.000Z","msg":"勝利人生!!!!勝利人生!!!!勝利人生!!!!"},{"pid":"748f76bc803b58f81ee4a25050109d780d4bb9fc","tid":2081032,"uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"好撚老土<br />\n個大佬有個車頂唔用特登淋雨<br />\n又畫到食煙好似好撚型<br />\n<br />\n80年代咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e8d4bcbfaa0c84e1862e565edccfa4c8e7b0b7","tid":2081032,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"勝利人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05bda98e77ce777b48a2a2767fd17de1c328b68","tid":2081032,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"有冇膠袋都無所謂啦，之前果本打拳仔期期都係神人隻揪之嘛，洗咩入膠袋姐，呢本就咁睇第一期咪又係同打拳仔一樣，如果係水深哥編劇就要入膠袋喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9c7e6af1aa9e68e45666244465fb31b643539e","tid":2081032,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"1925年原來係孫文死<br />\n仲有5月三十血腥鎮壓"},{"pid":"68052f341d95387332ddb72a51d557a9528bdbca","tid":2081032,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748f76bc803b58f81ee4a25050109d780d4bb9fc","tid":2081032,"uid":4493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"好撚老土<br />\n個大佬有個車頂唔用特登淋雨<br />\n又畫到食煙好似好撚型<br />\n<br />\n80年代咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:34:05.000Z","msg":"佢今次醒目,知道自己脫節,唔用現代做背境"},{"pid":"28946b64b02b78875ed726d59260bc4c86ebe461","tid":2081032,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"其實有樣野好好奇<br />\n<br />\n人力車可以有幾快?<br />\n<br />\n一個人要拖住架車，上面仲坐左個人，